  "Lucio Tan is the founder and chairman of the $2 billion (sales) LT group, which has interests in tobacco, spirits, banking and property development. ",
  "In 1982, Tan established Asia Brewery. Now a subsidiary of LT, the brewery was the only one then to compete with the market leader San Miguel.",
  "His eldest son Michael is president of LT group.",
  "Tan's grandson Lucio Tan III was appointed as vice president of loss-making Philippines Airlines in May 2021."
